If rumors are to be believed, a new Municipal Manager was appointed last night. Mobserver.co.za has learned from a trusted source that Theo van Vuuren, dubbed ‘Mr Fix It’when he started at the troubled eMalahleni  municpality, was appointed as acting Municipal Manager at the Steve Tshwete Local Municipality. It recently came to light that an outside candidate might be appointed in the place of acting Municipal Manager Mandla Mnguni. Van Vuuren has been wrapped in controversy after allegations that he spent R20 mil on body guards.